A very basic streaming app that does:

1. Read json files using flume into kafka
2. Do light weight transformation from one kafka topic to another using flink
3. Pull data from flink into Linkedin's Pinot
4. View the data in Pinot's web UI 

Resources:

http://kafka.apache.org
http://flume.apache.org
http://flink.apache.org
https://github.com/linkedin/pinot

Steps in the file sales-streaming/src/main/resources/run_steps
